source: TEXT_REGOTH3REUNION_00416_SYSTEM_000_011<tab>Gazing into Ozbeg's cold, dead eyes, you realize that he is responsible for monitoring the merchants that trade in Reunion.
target: TEXT_REGOTH3REUNION_00416_SYSTEM_000_011<tab>Dieser Mann scheint den Handel in Reunion zu überwachen.

source: TEXT_REGOTH3REUNION_00416_SYSTEM_000_023<tab>Unflinching, Ozbeg continues to stare into the distance. You turn and notice that he has his eyes locked on the marketplace. It appears Reunion is used by traders from all over to sell their various wares.
target: TEXT_REGOTH3REUNION_00416_SYSTEM_000_023<tab>Ozbeg verzieht den Mund und blickt zu den Marktständen hinüber. Anscheinend dient Reunion den Händlern der Region als Umschlagplatz für ihre Waren.
